{"meta":{"title":"Mut's blog","subtitle":null,"description":"记录自己","author":"Mut","url":"http://yoursite.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"categories","date":"2019-07-17T06:44:48.000Z","updated":"2019-07-17T06:44:48.306Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"tags","date":"2019-07-17T06:44:37.000Z","updated":"2019-07-19T02:27:09.630Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"hexo 4000端口被占用问题解决","slug":"hexo-4000端口被占用","date":"2019-07-19T03:03:48.000Z","updated":"2019-07-19T04:17:31.366Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/07/19/hexo-4000端口被占用/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/07/19/hexo-4000端口被占用/","excerpt":"","text":"问题描述：修改blog文件夹位置之后，执行hexo s 部署服务器时显示端口4000被占用 解决方法: 使用如下部署命令，将端口号改为5000$ hexo s -p 5000 修改站点配置文件 打开hexo-server文件夹内的index.js文件 将port值修改为5000","categories":[{"name":"问题记录","slug":"问题记录","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/问题记录/"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/hexo/"}]},{"title":"markdown 问题记录","slug":"markdown-问题记录","date":"2019-07-19T03:03:48.000Z","updated":"2019-07-19T03:53:27.024Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/07/19/markdown-问题记录/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/07/19/markdown-问题记录/","excerpt":"","text":"1. 设置图片大小正常图片引用示例1![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Mut1/picture/master/picgo/md出错.png) markdown语法调整图片大小标准的markdown，在图片后面加上“=100x100” ，就能实现图片大小调整。但这种hexo不支持。 使用img标签，设置图片大小：123&lt;div align=center&gt; &lt;img width=400 src=&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Mut1/picture/master/picgo/md出错.png&quot; &gt;&lt;/div&gt;","categories":[{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/笔记/"}],"tags":[{"name":"markdown","slug":"markdown","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/markdown/"}]},{"title":"hexo 安装问题记录","slug":"hexo问题记录","date":"2019-07-16T05:41:15.000Z","updated":"2019-07-19T03:54:08.192Z","comments":true,"path":"2019/07/16/hexo问题记录/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/07/16/hexo问题记录/","excerpt":"","text":"1. 开启indigo主题的tag页 在blog文件夹下输入命令：hexo new page tags 修改文件：hexo/source/tags/index.md 添加代码：layout：tags 2. md无法解析，hexo s出错 解决方法： 使用vim打开markdown文件，查看是否有错误字符","categories":[{"name":"问题记录","slug":"问题记录","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/问题记录/"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/hexo/"},{"name":"indigo","slug":"indigo","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/indigo/"}]}]}